---
import Page from "@deckup/astro/page";
---

<Page title="Deckup for Astro">
  <h1>Deckup for Astro</h1>
  <p>Mount slide decks inside an Astro documentation site without giving up host routing.</p>
</Page>

<Page title="Host-safe integration">
  <h1>Host-safe integration</h1>
  <ul>
    <li>Decks are selected by glob.</li>
    <li>Each deck receives its own injected route.</li>
    <li>The host Astro app keeps ownership of root, srcDir, output, and adapters.</li>
  </ul>
</Page>
